<textHTML>&lt;p&gt;At the end of the lecture&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Ask students a question which can be either pre-made or improvised based on the lecture. The types of questions posed are as follows:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Review a concept just discussed in class (can be a problem that has to be solved)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Discuss a concept or fact in the lecture that was unclear&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Receive student feedback on course material, approaches, strategies, the instructorâ€™s performance, etc.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;</textHTML>
