<textHTML>&lt;p&gt;Before the next class&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Review all of the submitted answers.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;If the question was based on:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;A concept: tabulate the percentage of correct and incorrect answers&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;A concept that was unclear: prepare a quick lesson for the beginning of the class to clarify misconceptions&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Course material, approaches, strategies or instructor performance: use the feedback to adjust how the course is run or what the instructor is doing&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;</textHTML>
